## Execution

### Training
```bash
./Q1/train.sh <output_dir>
./Q2/train.sh <output_dir>
# Q3 has no training
```

### Inference
```bash
./Q1/infer.sh <en|hi|kn> <test_file> <output_dir>
./Q2/infer.sh <en|hi|kn|or|tcy> <test_file> <output_dir>
./Q3/infer.sh <hi|kn|or|tcy> <test_file> <output_dir>
```

